SUMMARY:The First Look Fête
DESCRIPTION:Friday evening culminates in an elegant\, high-end cocktail celebration honoring the extraordinary generosity and bold vision that brought the Stevens & Smith Center to life. This exclusive\, ticketed event brings together our closest supporters for a night of gratitude and recognition\, just next door in the newly renovated Commons on Vine.\n\nGuests will enjoy curated cocktails\, elevated fare\, lively entertainment\, and one of the very first opportunities to experience the Center up close. It’s more than a party\, it’s a toast to the partners and donors who made history possible\, and a sparkling first look at what’s ahead.\n\n \n\nTickets coming soon!
URL:https://stevensandsmithcenter.org/event/first-look-fete/
LOCATION:Commons on Vine\, Lancaster County Convention Center\, 19 E. Vine Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://stevensandsmithcenter.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Fete_Web.png
